OL,3,CD-Day veterans' children make Normandy
OL,4,Cpilgrimage so legacy lives on
OL,6,FITV Granada Reports' has been speaking
OL,7,Fto the families of D-Day veterans as
OL,8,Fthey prepare for the 80th anniversary
OL,9,Fof the seaborne invasion.
OL,11,FThe children of late war veterans have
OL,12,Ftravelled to France to make sure their
OL,13,Fparents' sacrifices are never
OL,14,Fforgotten.
OL,16,FThe (NVA) consisted of ordinary men
OL,17,Fand women who played a role in an
OL,18,Fextraordinary moment during the Second
OL,19,FWorld War.
