OL,3,CD-Day veterans' children make Normandy
OL,4,Cpilgrimage so legacy lives on
OL,6,F6 June 2024 marks 80 years since the
OL,7,Flargest invasion that has ever taken
OL,8,Fplace by sea, land and air, when
OL,9,FAllied forces landed on the beaches to
OL,10,Fdefeat Nazi Germany.
OL,12,FWhile the passage of time means no
OL,13,Fmembers of the NVA survive, a legacy
OL,14,Fgroup of younger generations is
OL,15,Fensuring their loved ones remain part
OL,16,Fof the commemorations.
