OL,3,CD-Day veterans' children make Normandy
OL,4,Cpilgrimage so legacy lives on
OL,6,FOver a dozen made the pilgrimage from
OL,7,FGreater Manchester to attend a special
OL,8,Fveterans' service at Coleville-
OL,9,FMontgomery ahead of the anniversary
OL,10,Fitself.
OL,12,FThey are visiting the five landing
OL,13,Fbeaches and sending live images back
OL,14,Fhome, alongside archive recordings
OL,15,Ffrom those who fought.
