OL,3,CD-Day veterans' children make Normandy
OL,4,Cpilgrimage so legacy lives on
OL,6,FKen Benbow, 98, has previously been
OL,7,Famong the veterans in Normandy for the
OL,8,Fanniversary.
OL,10,FFormer Royal Naval officer Ken Benbow,
OL,11,F98, from Kirkham, Lancashire has
OL,12,Fpreviously taken part in anniversary
OL,13,Fcommemorations in Normandy.
OL,15,FHe was aboard one of nearly 7,000
OL,16,Fvessels which crossed the English
OL,17,FChannel on 6 June 1944.
OL,19,FHMS Crane's task was to protect Allied
OL,20,Fships, landing craft and troops
OL,21,Flanding on the beaches of Normandy.
